name: General Walex Blissex (V)
Lore: 'Engineer who worked with Jan Dodonna to design the A-wing starfighter. Given honorary rank due to his service to the Rebellion.',
Text: 'Adds 1 to power of anything he pilots. While piloting a capital starship at a battleground system, in each battle a player''s first battle destiny draw may not be canceled or reduced and if opponent canceled a just drawn battle destiny, they lose 1 Force.',
